#define ANIMESH_STRENGTH 80000
#define STAND "Explosive animation - Speed Punch"
#define LAND "Explosive animation - Male Crouch Pose 4"
#define WALK "Explosive animation - Walk 40 Male Cool"

#define GREETINGS ["You? They sent me you? I’ve coughed harder than the strike it will take to unmake you.","Don't bother begging. It won't save you, and frankly, your voice already irritates me.","I am going to close my eyes. If you aren't dead by the time I open them, I’ll make it hurt.","Look at you, trembling. You aren't a battle. You're a chore.","I’d tell you to run, but my boots are already dirty and I’d rather not chase a bug.","That's a very shiny weapon you have there. Let's see how deep I can shove it down your throat.","You think you're a hero on your little world, don't you? Let me show you how fragile your world really is.","I’ll give you one free strike. Make it count, because my turn will be your last.","A brave posture! I love it when they think they have a chance right before the ribs snap.","You're just meat. Just another pile of meat waiting to be tenderized.","Alright, you look like you can take a punch. Let's find out how many it takes to liquefy your organs!","Don't hold back now! I want to feel the resistance when my fist passes through your chest!","Viltrum demands your submission, but personally? I really, really hope you refuse.","Ah, a proper little soldier. Come on then, let's see what happens when an immovable object meets me!","I’ve broken entire empires of people just like you. You're all the same color on the inside.","Yes! That’s it! That's the look of someone who might actually make me sweat! Come on!","Finally, a real fight! Try to aim for my cybernetic arm, I want to see if you can rip it off!","I haven't felt this kind of killing intent in decades! Don't disappoint me, warrior!","You think you can save your people from me? Good! Fight like your entire species depends on it!","Let’s skip the talking. I want to hear the sound of your skull cracking against my knuckles!","Hahaha! Fantastic! A monster capable of tearing a world apart! Let's see who breaks first!","I don't care about the Viltrum Empire right now. Right now, it's just you, me, and a whole lot of agony!","Paint the sky with my blood if you can! I want to see how far you can push me!","You have the eyes of a butcher. Splendid! Let us see who handles the knife better!","I’ve lived for thousands of years for battles like this! Give me everything you have!","You walk with the strength of a dying star! Perfect! Let's find out if a god can choke on his own teeth!","Even if you tear my head from my shoulders, this will be the greatest day of my life! DIE!","Show me what real power is! Force me to fight for my miserable life! DO IT!","A force of nature! I am going to tear you apart piece by piece, or die trying!","No terms, no surrender! Just pure, beautiful, unrestricted slaughter!","You think your divinity makes you safe from a Viltrumite?! I will drag you down to hell with me!","Unmake reality if you want, but I’m going to bite your throat out before the void takes us!","A god of creation? Let's see how you handle a god of destruction!","(Maniacal, unhinged laughter) Tear my atoms apart! Smash my soul! I am Conquest, and I will paint your heavens red!","The ultimate prey... Come on, almighty one! Let’s see if a god can feel absolute terror!"]

#define WrestleWin ["Pathetic. I didn't even have to fly to catch you.","You snapped like a dry twig. I’ve had harder warm-ups in my sleep.","A waste of my time, a waste of my breath, and a waste of a good pair of boots.","I barely tapped you and your skull turned to mush. Disappointing.","They told me you were a warrior. Apparently, your people don't know the definition of the word.","Look at you, choking on your own blood. Was that little rebellion worth it?","You thought that little toy weapon would save you from a Viltrumite? Hilarious.","You had a spark of spirit, I'll give you that. Too bad your body was made of glass.","I told you to make your free strike count. Now look at you.","Just another corpse to add to the tally. Next time, send someone who can actually bruise me.","You fought well for a mortal, but 'well' doesn't stop a fist from passing through your spine.","Ah, the sweet sound of a ribcage collapsing. Never gets old.","You chose the hard way, and now your world belongs to Viltrum. Praise your own stubbornness.","You put up a decent fight. It's a shame you ran out of blood so quickly.","A respectable effort. Now lie there and watch your empire burn.","Hahaha! Now that was a slaughter! You actually made my knuckles ache!","You tore my flesh! Look at this! Magnificent! Too bad I heal and you... well, you don't.","I haven't had a smile like this on my face in fifty years. Thank you for dying so beautifully!","You fought like a rabid animal! I loved every second of breaking your spirit!","You almost held your own. If you had a few more centuries to train, you might have actually lived.","YES! Look at us! We painted the whole damn continent red! What a glorious day!","You shattered my cybernetic arm! You absolute monster! I am going to cherish this scar forever!","I haven't been pushed this close to the edge in an eternity! God, it feels good to be alive!","You fought for your entire species, and you still lost. Taste that despair—it's sweeter than the blood!","You were magnificent! A true titan! But in the end... nobody beats Conquest!","(Maniacal, wheezing laughter) I killed a god! I tore his throat out with my bare teeth!","Look at you... cosmic absolute... rotting in the dirt just like the rest of them!","My heart nearly stopped three times! You almost had me! Oh, the sheer, beautiful thrill of it!","You wielded the stars, but my fists wielded pure, unadulterated hatred! Guess which one won?!","This battle will be sung about in the halls of Viltrum for ten thousand years! And I am the one who survived!","You unmade creation... but you couldn't unmake me! (Coughs up blood, laughing)","Even a supreme being can be choked to death if you hold their neck hard enough!","I dragged a deity into the mud and butchered it! I am Conquest! I am the end of all things!","(Deafening, unhinged roar) I survived the void! I broke the almighty! I am the ultimate conqueror!","Reality belongs to the strongest... and today... that's me..."]

#define WrestleDefeat ["You didn't fight me! You used tricks! Coward! Stand still and let me tear your face off!","This... this poison... My cells are melting... You pathetic, weak piece of trash...","A trap?! You trapped me like an animal?! Look at me! Fight me like a man!","I will find a way out of this machine, and when I do, I will spend a century flaying you alive!","No... I am Conquest! I do not fall to a bug! I do not—ugh!","What is this sound?! My ears... my balance... Stop that noise and fight me!","A weapon that can pierce my skin? Where did a primitive piece of garbage like you find that?!","You caught me off guard... a lucky strike. It won't happen again... I'll strip the meat from your bones...","My own arrogance... I let you hit me. (Spits blood) You think this makes you a warrior?!","Ugh... you broke my mechanical arm... Enjoy your little victory, because your world is still going to burn.","You aimed for my old scars... Smart. But you've only made my death more expensive for you.","I underestimated your resolve. You let me break your ribs just to get a clean shot at my throat...","Go on then! Finish it! But know that Viltrum will turn your oceans to boiling blood for this!","My vision is fading... physical limits... a concept I haven't felt in a millennium.","You won the day, soldier. But you look just as broken as I am. Enjoy your hollow victory.","Hahaha! Look at my chest... you completely caved it in! What a magnificent strike!","I can feel my skull fracturing... Yes! That's it! Put everything you have into the next one!","You fought like a rabid dog to save this pathetic planet. I respect that... now choke me out...","You're covered in my blood... and I'm covered in yours. God, what a beautiful way to go...","I'm falling... but I took half your face with me. I'll see you in hell, boy.","You tore my good arm completely off... (Wheezes, coughing blood)... You really are a monster...","Even with all my Viltrumite might... I couldn't break you. You are a true god of slaughter.","My heart is failing... the thrill is finally over. Do it... snap my neck...","I haven't felt pain like this since the scourge virus... It's almost nostalgic...","You beat me... but you had to become a butcher to do it. Welcome to my world.","(Guttural, unhinged laughter) Yes! Smash my atoms! This is the death I always wanted!","You wield the power of a star... and it feels... so... warm... (Smiles as he burns)","I spent thousands of years killing... it's only fair... someone finally killed me...","You didn't just beat me... you erased me. Magnificent... absolutely magnificent...","My body is turning to ash... but my soul is laughing... What a fight...","You can unmake my reality... but you can't unmake the fact that I bit your hand, you cosmic bastard!","So this is the end of all things... I'm glad I spent my final moments trying to tear your throat out.","(Maniacal laughter fading into the void) I don't care if you're God! I didn't bow! I never bowed!","You are everything... and I am just meat... yet I still made you bleed...","Bury me in the void... I’ve earned my rest..."]
